name: Try to Jump
description:
Reckless square rushes to conquer the universe. Try it and you! Use the power of the Jedi to become the best jumper.

* Test your reaction.
* Jump as possible.
* Pay attention.
* Obstacles to jump.

To complete all levels we need your belief in success.
